      "review_summary": "The PR changes auth token export/listing so export can use a non-migrating token read and auth list stops fallback keyring traversal after keyring timeouts.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main exports through the migrating token getter and auth-list fallback can call Keys plus per-token GetToken after list errors. I did not run a live failing current-main Keychain prompt scenario, but maintainer terminal proof confirms the after-fix macOS Keychain path at a reviewed PR head.",
